name: pytest-runner
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "6.0.0" %}

package:
  name: pytest-runner
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/p/pytest-runner/pytest-runner-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: b4d85362ed29b4c348678de797df438f0f0509497ddb8c647096c02a6d87b685

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.7
    - pip
    - setuptools-scm >=3.4.1
  run:
    - python >=3.7
    - setuptools
    - pytest

test:
  imports:
    - ptr
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest-runner
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Invoke py.test as distutils command with dependency resolution.
  dev_url: https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest-runner

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - dopplershift
    - ocefpaf
